<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4021.4.9>
    bibo:endPage "596" ;
    bibo:issue "4" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "591" ;
    bibo:volume "4021" ;
    dc:creator "Laborda, Álvaro; Simó, Miguel" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "Description of the female of Eutichurus ibiuna Bonaldo, 1994 (Araneae: Eutichuridae) with notes on natural history and sexual behavior" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.243208>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.243209>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.243210>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.243211> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.243208>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Eutichurus ibiuna, genitalia: A left palp, prolateral view; B same, ventral view; C same, retrolateral view; D epigynum, ventral view; E cleared vulva, dorsal view. Abbreviations: A = atrium; AE = apical spermatheca; AL = anterior lobe; BE = basal spermatheca; E = embolus; EP = embolar process; FD = fertilization duct; PP = posterior plate; RTA = retrolateral tibial apophysis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/243208/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.243209>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Live specimens of Eutichurus ibiuna: A male (FCE-Ar 6204); B female (FCE-Ar 4809)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/243209/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.243210>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Geographic distribution of Eutichurus ibiuna: literature record = blue circle; new records = red circles." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/243210/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.243211>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Eutichurus ibiuna, behavior: A juvenile in its silk retreat; B mating position; C couple during mating (note the silk deposited by the male over the female)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/243211/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

